<template>
  <label>{{ $event.target.value }}</label>
  <input
    v-bind:value="value"
    v-on:input="$emit('input', $event.target.value)"
    type="text"
  />
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "MisaInput",
  props: ["value"],
  methods: {
    emitValueChanged() {
      this.$emit("input-value-changed", this.value);
    },
  },

  data() {
    return {};
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
